About the Business

Business owner information

Jeff A.

Business Owner

Loaded toppings, a freshly baked crust and tasty secret sauce pair wonderfully with a cold craft brew at Woodstock's Pizza, where legendary pizza meets epic party. Customize your pizza any way you like it with gourmet sauces, toppings and whole wheat or gluten-free crusts! We also have vegetarian and vegan options. Whether you're looking for a family friendly location, a place to watch sports or a fun atmosphere, you can find it at Woodstock's Pizza. We also have a large patio. Stop by for our legendary cheesy WildeBread or dreamlike sugary CinnaBread and hang out with the Woodstock's family. Bingo & Brews: Every Tuesday, 8 PM Come for the half-priced pints, stay for the free fun & prizes! Trivia Night: Every Thursday, 5 PM - Midnight Teams of 2-6, check Facebook for themes. Fun prizes for winners! Friday Night Alive: Every Friday, 10 PM Let your inner rockstar and come jam out! Play what we have here or bring your own gear Live Music: Every Saturday, 10 PM Featuring different local bands every Saturday evening in the bar!…

    Elite '2021

    Phoenix, AZ
    118
    95

    10/22/2018

    I am thoroughly impressed with this place. I ordered the Meat Orgy pizza and tried three flavors of wings. I think the seasonings were Honey Mustard, Buffalo, and a spice rub. The wings were my favorite part of the order...the meat just fell off the bone, and every flavor was mouthwatering! The pizza was delicious, although I would have preferred a bit less cheese. I'm not a big fan of huge dollops of cheese. The crust was thick and soft. I normally don't like a really thick crust, but it was balanced perfectly with the overloaded toppings.

    I can't wait to come back here. I saw that they have different events going on each week, like bingo and trivia. It sounds like so much fun! They also have great deals on pints of beer. Just a really cool place to grab dinner with friends and get involved with the community.

    Business owner information

    Samantha L.

    Business Manager

    10/25/2018

    What an incredible review, thanks for all the love Elizabeth, we appreciate it!

    Also just wanted to give a quick run down of weekly events for anyone that is curious:
    Tue = Bingo & Brews @ 8 PM (Half-Priced Pints & Free Bingo with prizes!)
    Wed = Woodstock's Speaks @ 9 PM (Featuring poetry, monologues, etc.)
    Thu= Trivia Night @ 9 PM (there are weekly themes, prizies, and more)
    Fri = Friday Night Alive @ 10 PM (an all out jam session, you can bring your own gear or play what we have here)
    Sat = Local Live Music @ 10 PM (featuring a different band most Saturday Nights)

Frequently Asked Questions about Woodstock's Pizza Davis

Does Woodstock's Pizza Davis take reservations?

Yes, you can make a reservation by picking a date, time, and party size.

Does Woodstock's Pizza Davis have outdoor seating?

Yes, Woodstock's Pizza Davis has outdoor seating.

Is Woodstock's Pizza Davis currently offering delivery or takeout?

Yes, Woodstock's Pizza Davis offers both delivery and takeout.

Woodstock's Pizza Davis accepts credit cards.
